<h3>Notes</h3>
<ul>
    <li>When pawn lands in same sector as other pawns, the newly-moved pawn is placed ahead of all others</li>
    <li>Return 3 Dwarf Planet theory tokens for a standard game</li>
    <li>May only survey or target the visible sky</li>
    <li>Target: two per game</li>
    <li>Research: may not perform consecutive research actions</li>
</ul>

